## ModelRole Classification (lemonade.rs)

`LemonadeModelEntry::role()` classifies models. **FLM recipe is checked first** so NPU models are never misclassified as GPU variants:

| Role | Recipe | Key Labels | Hardware |
|---|---|---|---|
| `NpuEmbedding` | `flm` | `embeddings` | AMD NPU |
| `NpuStt` | `flm` | `audio` / `transcription` | AMD NPU |
| `NpuLlm` | `flm` | `reasoning` / `tool-calling` / `coding` | AMD NPU |
| `CpuTts` | `kokoro` | `tts` / `speech` | CPU |
| `GpuStt` | `whispercpp` | `transcription` (non-FLM) | GPU/Vulkan |
| `GpuLlm` | `llamacpp` | `reasoning` / `tool-calling` / `vision` / `coding` | GPU ROCm/Vulkan |
| `LlamacppEmbedding` | `llamacpp` | `embeddings` | CPU/GPU |
| `Reranker` | `llamacpp` | `reranking` | GPU/CPU |
| `ImageGen` | `sd-cpp` | `image` | GPU |

Registry selector methods: `npu_embedding_model()`, `npu_stt_model()`, `npu_llm_model()`, `tts_model()`, `stt_model()` (GpuStt only), `llm_model()` (GpuLlm only), `reranker_model()`, `llamacpp_embedding_model()`, `all_llamacpp_embedding_models()`.